Evening Folks,

   I have a bit of money in my PayPal account and am wondering if I might be able to turn it into a few more C46s for my set.  I'm at 57/90 so far, and would love to break the 60 mark before summer hits and baseball cards take a back seat to sunshine and actual baseball games.

That said, I'm looking for vg-ish cards raw or graded.  I have a few duplicate C46s and a couple others T-s I can trade too if folks are interested.

Thanks for looking!

Richard.
